{"tid":1927824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣有人去派出所做證人，遭警員將酒精當額溫槍顏射","createTime":"2020-03-16T04:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T04:33:45.000Z","uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"671aa4036e101054a76bdaba7a49baba6a47a878","tid":1927824,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1668008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253fnews_id%3D1668008&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=2a011e26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1668008</a><br />\n<br />\n近來台灣因新冠肺炎（COVID-19）疫情病例增多，各機關進出都要量體溫、消毒增強防疫力度，結果台北市有名民眾因協助處理民眾糾紛要到派出所做證人，進入北市警中正一分局忠孝西路派出所時，執行檢疫的警員對他量體溫並提供酒精消毒<br />\n<br />\n但因當時警所內太忙，<span style=\"color: red;\">警員忙中有錯，一手持額溫槍、一手持酒精，本來要量額溫後提供手部酒精消毒，但警員卻錯把酒精噴罐當額溫槍往該民眾頭臉噴去</span>，這名熱心民眾慘遭警員「顏射」酒精入眼，痛苦不堪，警員見狀致歉再三，趕緊協助民眾到洗手間以清水沖眼緩和不適狀態。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0RpMQso.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0RpMQso.jpg&h=381b073b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}